There are major changes and many new features in version 16 of
the model suit. Some highlites are:

Semi-Lagrangian tracer transport in Planet Simulator
Improvements in nearly all parameterisation modules
New boundary data for T21, T31, and T42 resolutions with
references (AMIP-II, GTOPO30, etc.)

New alternating grid for symmetry conserving Legendre-transformation in PUMA.
New diagnostics for PUMA (Maximum Entropy)

Shallow Atmosphere Model (SAM)

New postprocessor "burn6" with easier usage and enhanced NetCDF support.

And many more (read the manuals !!!)

